# =========================================================
# Static DNS Records
# =========================================================
# Format: IP    FQDN
# One entry per line. Changes are picked up on dnsmasq restart.
#
# Examples:
# 100.100.100.10    whoami.test.lab.example.com
# 100.100.100.10    traefik.test.lab.example.com
# 100.100.100.20    app.dev.lab.example.com
